1)Create a table in database
CREATE TABLE `java`.`customer` (
  `id` INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `first_name` VARCHAR(45) NULL,
  `last_name` VARCHAR(45) NULL,
  `email` VARCHAR(45) NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`));

Make sure ur id column in the database table is autoincrement.

2) Create maven-webaapp 

3) Add the following in your pom.xml

